    "      \"Total Return: 51402.73 (514.03%)\\n\",\n",
    "      \"Mean Bet-To-Bet Return: 0.1%\\n\",\n",
    "      \"Volatility (standard deviation) of Bet-To-Bet Returns: 0.9%\\n\",\n",
    "      \"Downside Volatility of Returns: 0.52%\\n\",\n",
    "      \"Kurtosis of Returns: -0.29\\n\",\n",
    "      \"Maximum Drawdown: -38.8% over 392 games\\n\",\n",
    "      \"Sharpe Ratio: 0.11595591401815317\\n\",\n",
    "      \"Sortino Ratio: 0.20150549338769952\\n\",\n",
    "      \"Calmar Ratio: 13.246773079381109\\n\"\n",
    "     ]\n",
    "    }\n",
    "   ],\n",
